 <title>Você que fez ou tudo foi feito na China?</title>
 <link>http://mutgamb.org/blog/Voce-que-fez-ou-tudo-foi-feito-na-China</link>
 <description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Do que adianta saber o nome de todos os componentes de uma placa m&amp;atilde;e, almejar o mercado de trabalho e n&amp;atilde;o se apropriar da l&amp;oacute;gica que a tecnologia tem sob nossas rela&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es?&lt;/strong&gt; @ Isaac Filho.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Podemos conhecer objetos de qualquer tipo somente na medida em que somos capazes de produzi-los&lt;/strong&gt;. @Werner Stark, em The Sociology of Knowledge.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Webert voltou a puxar a conversa do&lt;a href=&quot;http://mutgamb.org/blog/Plaquinhas&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt; Raspberry Pi&lt;/a&gt;, mostrando &lt;a href=&quot;http://http://globotv.globo.com/globo-news/globo-news-ciencia-e-tecnologia/v/criancas-aprendem-programacao-atraves-de-um-dos-menores-computadores-do-mundo/2179234/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;esse v&amp;iacute;deo&lt;/a&gt;. Enquanto isso, em threads paralelas mas n&amp;atilde;o dissociadas...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mbraz compartilhou &lt;a href=&quot;http://va.mu/YEUR&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;imagens das oficinas&lt;/a&gt; que &lt;a href=&quot;http://mutgamb.org/blog/Oficinas-de-Metareciclagem-em-Osasco&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;aconteceram em Osasco&lt;/a&gt;...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;rtecenter&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://mutgamb.org/sites/mutgamb.org/files/mbraz.JPG&quot; style=&quot;height: 315px; width: 420px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Marcos Egito as &lt;a href=&quot;http://maregito.wordpress.com/2012/10/08/i-experimentacao-na-de-robotica-livre-na-concha-colaborativa/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;experimenta&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es colaborativas&lt;/a&gt; e &lt;a href=&quot;http://konesans.tk/?p=795&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;as intera&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es do Konesans&lt;/a&gt;...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;rtecenter&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://maregito.files.wordpress.com/2012/10/dsc00021.jpg?w=700&amp;amp;h=&quot; style=&quot;height: 315px; width: 420px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Glerm linkou &lt;a href=&quot;http://crystal.xxn.org.uk/wiki/doku.php?id=the_crystal_world:space:postdescription&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;meios DIY do The Crystal World Open Laboratory and Exhibition&lt;/a&gt; para fazer plasma, microondas, precipta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e extra&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o mineral, entre outras experi&amp;ecirc;ncias interessantes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;rtecenter&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://crystal.xxn.org.uk/wiki/lib/exe/fetch.php?w=968&amp;amp;media=the_crystal_world:space:dsc_0152.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height: 236px; width: 420px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
