 <title>Reciências</title>
 <link>http://mutgamb.org/blog/Reciencias</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;Marcelo Braz compartilhou a digitaliza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o dos &lt;a href=&quot;http://http://www.popsci.com/archives&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;140 de arquivos da revista Popular Science&lt;/a&gt;. Cleber trouxe um artigo sobre &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.theatlantic.com/technology/archive/2012/06/a-perfect-and-beautiful-machine-what-darwins-theory-of-evolution-reveals-about-artificial-intelligence/258829/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;evolucionismo e tecnologias&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
